{"tid":356462,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"欣宜透視裙露高叉緊身衣 現大腿玫瑰紋身","createTime":"2017-08-12T05:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T06:09:03.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"886abf89c961e854329272127bfab181210d30e2","tid":356462,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/afbzAXCxm0S_udEJNa5EmQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170812f105521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FafbzAXCxm0S_udEJNa5EmQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170812f105521.jpg&h=1e965746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】鄭欣宜、陳嘉桓(Rose)、冼國林、 朱慧敏、馬德鐘夫婦、麥長青等出席仁濟醫院「海外學生仁濟夜2017」慈善餐舞會，欣宜身穿透視裙透現內里高叉緊身衣，並發現她左邊大腿多了一個玫瑰紋身。欣宜表示紋了好幾年，當年與曲奇店拍檔打賭若賺取某金額就去紋身，竟然真的達到該生意額，她紋了店舖曲奇味道「XO Rose」，是身上最大幅的一個紋身，但好友只在手上紋了一個哈哈笑，笑言被好友騙了。<br />\n<br />\n欣宜表示身上共有五個紋身，其他紋身大家永遠也看不到。有否愛的紋身?她說沒有，自認好穩陣，不會紋男友名字，因為紋身是一世的，除非結婚才考慮紋對方名，但也要先看另一半是否願意紋她的名字。會否紋子女名字?她說會，或可能是生日日期。欣宜指身上每個紋身都有特別意義，其中一個水仙花圖案是為紀念湊大她的外婆而紋，因公公叫婆婆做「水仙」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E6%AC%A3%E5%AE%9C%E9%80%8F%E8%A6%96%E8%A3%99%E9%9C%B2%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%89%E7%B7%8A%E8%BA%AB%E8%A1%A3-%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E8%85%BF%E7%8E%AB%E7%91%B0%E7%B4%8B%E8%BA%AB-024800823.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%25AE%259C%25E9%2580%258F%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A3%2599%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%258F%2589%25E7%25B7%258A%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%25A1%25A3-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2585%25BF%25E7%258E%25AB%25E7%2591%25B0%25E7%25B4%258B%25E8%25BA%25AB-024800823.html&d=eV%2FHGeCyAGOacYKnbfX0RTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0fc087d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E6%AC%A3%E5%AE%9C%E9%80%8F%E8%A6%96%E8%A3%99%E9%9C%B2%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%89%E7%B7%8A%E8%BA%AB%E8%A1%A3-%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E8%85%BF%E7%8E%AB%E7%91%B0%E7%B4%8B%E8%BA%AB-024800823.html</a>"},{"pid":"3ca341f18bdc2564e892019b998c58d320600a57","tid":356462,"uid":2287,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"金妹牌火腿q嘜認證？"},{"pid":"eac9a9c8ccbaa535ce9ef51d8d8d5a2af0d3a2c3","tid":356462,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:09:03.000Z","msg":"豬仔印"}]}